if they dont love her they might well fear her and her fellow 
aunties each day after getting together to read the official 
newspapers and study the latest government order the eight graying 
women split into pairs and divide up the neighborhood visiting 
stayathomes inquring about their health and other news 
mrs gao said it would be impossible for any fugitive student 
leaders to hide in her domain as soon as a stranger hits the 
neighborhood she said we will know right away questions are 
raised is he a friend where is he from did he register with 
police chinese law requires travelers to notify the local police 
station when staying away from home 
the houses on shady willow street are ancient onestory buildings 
built around small courtyards sometimes with a dozen families per 
unit each courtyard has a chief who knows what the families in his 
unit do where they go and who their friends and relatives are mrs 
gao said 
during the spring turmoil she said the chiefs checked up was 
soandso at home today where did he go when did he get back 
if someone took part in the protests the courtyard chief would 
know right away she said 
we cant guarantee everyone tells what they do said district 
official feng xiaomin gently correcting mrs gao its possible 
someone went out for a stroll and didnt say anything 
but nothing happened or they would have been arrested mrs 
gao shot back 
