tomsen said the advisers have orchestrated hundreds of scud 
missile firings and that some missiles hit pakistan scud has a 
range of up to 170 miles 
soviet personnel are also working in key afghan government 
ministries said tomsen 
he blamed the continued fighting in afghanistan on the soviet 
union 
washington will support a political settlement that removes najib 
and his marxist peoples democratic party of afghanistan from power 
millions of dollars in us military and humanitarian help have 
gone to the afghan guerrillas through pakistan which also harbors 
more than 3 million war refugees 
