deere amp co chairman robert a hanson has 
given up his title as chief executive officer after directing deere 
through its darkest days and into an era of record profits 
hanson 64 relinquished the companys reins wednesday to hans w 
becherer currently president of deere the world leader in tractor 
and agriculturalimplement manufacturing 
