<TEXT>
a former zzzz best co official was ordered to 
repay 224861 in illegal profits and interest from the fraudulent 
rugshampooing company and to pay triple damages of 674582 
jack n polevoi of woodland hills calif a former zzzz best 
vice president is serving an 18month prison sentence after 
pleading guilty in june to four counts of stock and tax fraud and 
other violations 
the order for polevoi to pay the nearly 900000 came wednesday 
from us district judge robert j kelleher it was based on 
findings that in mid1987 polevoi and his twin brother jerry ordered 
54200 shares of zzzz best to be sold short 
polevoi knew at the time that zzzz bests founder and chairman 
barry m minkow was considering resigning from the reseda 
califbased company which was crumbling 
when investors sell stock short they seek to profit from a 
decline in the stock price by selling borrowed shares and buying 
them back later zzzz best shares fell from more than 5 each at the 
time the short sales were made to 75 cents when polevoi completed 
the transactions 
polevoi and others also laundered 712000 in zzzz best corporate 
funds and bank loans through las vegas casinos in the days before 
the company collapsed 
minkow who convinced wall street and the public that he was a 
teenage business genius was convicted of 57 counts of fraud 
conspiracy and other violations after investigators discovered that 
much of the work supposedly done by zzzz best existed only on paper 
minkow is serving a 25year prison term and has been ordered to 
repay 26 million in illegal profits and restitution 
